▶️ How to Run

1. Open `erd.mwb` in MySQL Workbench to review the schema, or run `creating_data_base.sql` directly to build it
2. Import the source CSVs into the created tables
3. Run `data_cleaning.sql` to standardize types and handle nulls/blanks
4. Run `connection_betwen_tables.sql` to establish foreign key relationships
5. Run `Exploratory_Data_Analysis.sql` and `Analysis.sql` to reproduce the insights above

